      "source": [
        "# 第2章：Working with Text Data\n",
        "\n",
        "**目标：** 将原始文本转化为可供 LLM 训练使用的嵌入向量\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "原始文本 → 分词(Tokenization) → Token IDs → 嵌入向量 + 位置编码 → 模型输入\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 2.1 理解词嵌入（Word Embeddings）\n",
        "\n",
        "**核心问题：** 神经网络只能处理数字，如何让它理解文本？\n",
        "\n",
        "**方案演进：**\n",
        "1. **One-hot 编码** → 维度太高（词汇量=维度），且无法表达语义相似性\n",
        "2. **Word2Vec** → 固定的语义向量，但无法处理一词多义\n",
        "3. **LLM 嵌入** → 在训练过程中学习，同一个词在不同上下文中有不同表示\n",
        "\n",
        "> 💡 **关键洞察：** LLM 的嵌入层 (`nn.Embedding`) 本质是一个**可学习的查找表**——输入 token ID，输出对应的向量。这些向量在训练过程中不断更新。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "## 2.2 文本分词（Tokenizing Text）\n",
        "\n",
        "分词是 NLP 的第一步：把一段文本拆分成一个个小单元（token）。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 9,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "文本总长度: 20479 个字符\n",
            "前 200 个字符:\n",
            "I HAD always thought Jack Gisburn rather a cheap genius--though a good fellow enough--so it was no great surprise to me to hear that, in the height of his glory, he had dropped his painting, married a\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# 加载样本文本\n",
        "with open(\"../data/the-verdict.txt\", \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n",
        "    raw_text = f.read()\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"文本总长度: {len(raw_text)} 个字符\")\n",
        "print(f\"前 200 个字符:\\n{raw_text[:200]}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Hello!!world!!Is!this!!a!test!\n",
            "原始分割: ['Hello', ',', '', ' ', 'world', '.', '', ' ', 'Is', ' ', 'this', '--', '', ' ', 'a']\n",
            "清理后:   ['Hello', ',', 'world', '.', 'Is', 'this', '--', 'a', 'test', '?']\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import re\n",
        "\n",
        "# 用正则表达式分词\n",
        "# 括号 () 使分隔符也被保留在结果中\n",
        "pattern = r'([,.:;?_!\"()\\']|--|\\s)'\n",
        "\n",
        "text_sample = \"Hello, world. Is this-- a test?\"\n",
        "tokens = re.split(pattern, text_sample)\n",
        "print(f\"原始分割: {tokens[:15]}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 去掉空白 token\n",
        "tokens = [t.strip() for t in tokens if t.strip()]\n",
        "print(f\"清理后:   {tokens}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 10,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Token 总数: 4690\n",
            "前 30 个 token: ['I', 'HAD', 'always', 'thought', 'Jack', 'Gisburn', 'rather', 'a', 'cheap', 'genius', '--', 'though', 'a', 'good', 'fellow', 'enough', '--', 'so', 'it', 'was', 'no', 'great', 'surprise', 'to', 'me', 'to', 'hear', 'that', ',', 'in']\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# 对整篇文本分词\n",
        "all_tokens = re.split(pattern, raw_text)\n",
        "all_tokens = [t.strip() for t in all_tokens if t.strip()]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Token 总数: {len(all_tokens)}\")\n",
        "print(f\"前 30 个 token: {all_tokens[:30]}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### ✏️ 练习\n",
        "1. 试试去掉正则中的 `--`，看 `\"this-- a\"` 会怎么分词 <br>\n",
        "   替换后’this-- a‘ 会分词为’this--', 'a'\n",
        "\n",
        "2. 如果把 `\\s` 换成 ` `（只匹配空格），换行符会怎样？<br>\n",
        "   如果把`\\s` 换成 ` `（只匹配空格），换行不会进行分词，但是对于我们的text_sample，没有任何区别"
      ]
